{"to":["contact@communityinsights.org"],"subject":"Hawthorne University Alumni Contact Details for Post-Graduate Success Survey","body":"Hello Community Insights Team,

Per our partnership for the Hawthorne University post-graduate success survey, please find below the contact details for alumni who have provided consent to be invited to participate:

1. John Smith – john.smith@example.com – Software Engineer, TechCorp
2. Emily Johnson – emily.johnson@creative.com – Art Director, CreativeDesign
3. Michael Brown – michael.brown@financepro.com – Senior Financial Analyst, FinancePro
4. Sarah Davis – sarah.davis@healthware.com – Biotech Researcher, HealthWare

These individuals have agreed that their information may be shared with Community Insights solely for the purpose of administering this survey. Let me know if you require any additional information or formatting.

Best regards,
Jane 
Alumni Relations Coordinator
Hawthorne University"}
